surf_666



Map took way longer than it should have. Ran into limits at the same time that i started school. Eventually just decided to model literally everything that could be modeled so I could move on.

Meant for 66tick, 150aa, 10k maxvelocity. Somewhere around omnific in terms of difficulty.

Tier: 6
Stages: 6
Bonuses: 6

Bonus 1: Cyber
Bonus 2: Horsefeathers
Bonus 3: Krazy
Bonus 4: Phurix
Bonus 5: Doink Face
Bonus 6: Syncronyze

Thank you to all who tested the map, and to those who gave feedback.

Zones for timers

If anyone ports this to CS:GO, please contact me first. I plan on doing it on April 16th.
